<item>
            <title>[HBASE-9718] Add a test scope dependency on org.slf4j:slf4j-api to hbase-client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9718</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;hbase-client needs a test scope dependency on org.slf4j:slf4j-api in its POM. Without this change at least Eclipse cannot resolve org.slf4j.Logger from RecoverableZooKeeper - the ZooKeeper classes use it - and so the &apos;hbase-client&apos; project will not build. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
